{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01GFDP8sjUnDyec8S7jNuPXS","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good - the Jandex issue is gone. Now we have a new error: `Cannot place qualifiers on final fields: @Inject private final org.example.realworldapi.application.web.resource.UsersResource.tokenProvider`. Weld doesn't allow `@Inject` on `final` fields. This is likely because Lombok's `@RequiredArgsConstructor` makes fields `final`, and when Weld discovers these classes (with `bean-discovery-mode=\"all\"`), it sees `@Inject` on final fields.\n\nLet me check the UsersResource:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1222,"cache_read_input_tokens":54168,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1222,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":258},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d45be86e-3e5a-4433-b76a-a33ae6e615f7","uuid":"f9760b51-1f8e-445f-8616-573eb1365702"}
