{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014k46dVo26Dieysk4KcaErB","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.example.realworldapi;\n     2→\n     3→import io.undertow.Undertow;\n     4→import io.undertow.servlet.Servlets;\n     5→import io.undertow.servlet.api.DeploymentInfo;\n     6→import jakarta.enterprise.inject.spi.BeanManager;\n     7→import org.jboss.resteasy.cdi.CdiInjectorFactory;\n     8→import org.jboss.resteasy.core.ResteasyDeploymentImpl;\n     9→import org.jboss.resteasy.plugins.server.undertow.UndertowJaxrsServer;\n    10→import org.jboss.resteasy.spi.ResteasyDeployment;\n    11→import org.jboss.weld.environment.se.Weld;\n    12→import org.jboss.weld.environment.se.WeldContainer;\n    13→import org.slf4j.Logger;\n    14→import org.slf4j.LoggerFactory;\n    15→\n    16→import java.util.List;\n    17→\n    18→public class Main {\n    19→\n    20→    private static final Logger LOG = LoggerFactory.getLogger(Main.class);\n    21→\n    22→    public static void main(String[] args) throws Exception {\n    23→        int port = Integer.parseInt(System.getenv().getOrDefault(\"PORT\", \"8080\"));\n    24→        String host = System.getenv().getOrDefault(\"HOST\", \"0.0.0.0\");\n    25→\n    26→        // Initialize Weld CDI container\n    27→        Weld weld = new Weld();\n    28→        WeldContainer container = weld.initialize();\n    29→        LOG.info(\"CDI container initialized\");\n    30→\n    31→        // Verify JPA is ready by touching the EntityManagerFactory producer\n    32→        container.select(\n    33→            org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.persistence.EntityManagerProducer.class).get();\n    34→        LOG.info(\"JPA EntityManager ready\");\n    35→\n    36→        // Configure RESTEasy with CDI\n    37→        ResteasyDeployment deployment = new ResteasyDeploymentImpl();\n    38→        deployment.setInjectorFactoryClass(CdiInjectorFactory.class.getName());\n    39→\n    40→        // Register JAX-RS resource classes\n    41→        deployment.setScannedResourceClasses(List.of(\n    42→            \"org.example.realworldapi.application.web.resource.HealthResource\",\n    43→            \"org.example.realworldapi.application.web.resource.ArticlesResource\",\n    44→            \"org.example.realworldapi.application.web.resource.ProfilesResource\",\n    45→            \"org.example.realworldapi.application.web.resource.TagsResource\",\n    46→            \"org.example.realworldapi.application.web.resource.UserResource\",\n    47→            \"org.example.realworldapi.application.web.resource.UsersResource\"\n    48→        ));\n    49→\n    50→        // Register JAX-RS provider classes\n    51→        deployment.setScannedProviderClasses(List.of(\n    52→            \"org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.web.security.JwtSecurityFilter\",\n    53→            \"org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.web.security.RolesAllowedFilter\",\n    54→            \"org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.web.provider.JacksonConfigProvider\",\n    55→            \"org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.web.mapper.BeanValidationExceptionMapper\",\n    56→            \"org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.web.mapper.BusinessExceptionMapper\",\n    57→            \"org.example.realworldapi.infrastructure.web.mapper.GenericExceptionMapper\"\n    58→        ));\n    59→\n    60→        // Build Undertow deployment\n    61→        BeanManager beanManager = container.getBeanManager();\n    62→        DeploymentInfo di = new DeploymentInfo()\n    63→                .addServletContextAttribute(\n    64→                    ResteasyDeployment.class.getName(), deployment)\n    65→                .addServletContextAttribute(\n    66→                    \"jakarta.enterprise.inject.spi.BeanManager\", beanManager)\n    67→                .setContextPath(\"/api\")\n    68→                .setDeploymentName(\"ResteasyUndertow\")\n    69→                .setClassLoader(Main.class.getClassLoader())\n    70→                .addServlet(\n    71→                    Servlets.servlet(\"ResteasyServlet\",\n    72→                        org.jboss.resteasy.plugins.server.servlet.HttpServletDispatcher.class)\n    73→                        .setAsyncSupported(true)\n    74→                        .setLoadOnStartup(1)\n    75→                        .addMapping(\"/*\")\n    76→                );\n    77→\n    78→        UndertowJaxrsServer server = new UndertowJaxrsServer();\n    79→        server.start(\n    80→            Undertow.builder()\n    81→                .addHttpListener(port, host)\n    82→        );\n    83→        server.deploy(di);\n    84→\n    85→        LOG.info(\"RealWorld API started on port {}\", port);\n    86→        LOG.info(\"API available at http://{}:{}/api\", host, port);\n    87→\n    88→        Runtime.getRuntime().addShutdownHook(new Thread(() -> {\n    89→            LOG.info(\"Shutting down...\");\n    90→            server.stop();\n    91→            container.close();\n    92→        }));\n    93→    }\n    94→}\n    95→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d45be86e-3e5a-4433-b76a-a33ae6e615f7","uuid":"82537fc7-09d1-4ca7-a71c-f448f4d5dc38"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01XLVaJXCbzAGe81KcjErmf6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The issue is that we're using `Weld SE` (standalone) but need `Weld Servlet` to activate request scope for each HTTP request. I need to add the `org.jboss.weld.environment.servlet.Listener` to the deployment. Also, for the request scope to work, we need Weld Servlet integration. Let me add the listener:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1928,"cache_read_input_tokens":106567,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1928,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":708},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d45be86e-3e5a-4433-b76a-a33ae6e615f7","uuid":"076c85e7-fbe7-43f3-90d0-2c4d5e86c9b4"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01XLVaJXCbzAGe81KcjErmf6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01WB38ewKceNDHFxxRUo5zfC","name":"Edit","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/Main.java","old_string":"        // Build Undertow deployment\n        BeanManager beanManager = container.getBeanManager();\n        DeploymentInfo di = new DeploymentInfo()\n                .addServletContextAttribute(\n                    ResteasyDeployment.class.getName(), deployment)\n                .addServletContextAttribute(\n                    \"jakarta.enterprise.inject.spi.BeanManager\", beanManager)\n                .setContextPath(\"/api\")\n                .setDeploymentName(\"ResteasyUndertow\")\n                .setClassLoader(Main.class.getClassLoader())\n                .addServlet(\n                    Servlets.servlet(\"ResteasyServlet\",\n                        org.jboss.resteasy.plugins.server.servlet.HttpServletDispatcher.class)\n                        .setAsyncSupported(true)\n                        .setLoadOnStartup(1)\n                        .addMapping(\"/*\")\n                );","new_string":"        // Build Undertow deployment\n        BeanManager beanManager = container.getBeanManager();\n        DeploymentInfo di = new DeploymentInfo()\n                .addServletContextAttribute(\n                    ResteasyDeployment.class.getName(), deployment)\n                .addServletContextAttribute(\n                    \"jakarta.enterprise.inject.spi.BeanManager\", beanManager)\n                .setContextPath(\"/api\")\n                .setDeploymentName(\"ResteasyUndertow\")\n                .setClassLoader(Main.class.getClassLoader())\n                .addListener(\n                    Servlets.listener(\n                     