{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01S5zRMj141tDEduYymsxjg3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Complete: Quarkus -> Standalone Jakarta EE\n\n**Result: 22/22 smoke tests passing**\n\n### Key changes made in this session:\n1. **Fixed Docker BuildKit caching** - Added `ARG CACHE_BUST` to Dockerfile to force fresh file copies\n2. **Updated Main.java** to use Weld SE + RESTEasy `CdiInjectorFactory` with explicit resource/provider registration and Weld Servlet `Listener` for request scope activation\n3. **Simplified RestApplication.java** - Removed `getClasses()` override since resources are registered via `ResteasyDeployment`\n4. **Fixed CDI proxy issues** in `EntityUtils` and `SlugifySlugProvider` (switched from Lombok `@AllArgsConstructor` to `@Inject` field injection)\n5. **Resolved Jandex version conflict** between SmallRye Jandex 3.x (required by Hibernate) and old `org.jboss:jandex:2.x` (from RESTEasy transitive deps)\n6. **Fixed HealthResource** to return raw JSON strings instead of `Map.of()` to avoid Jackson `WRAP_ROOT_VALUE` wrapping\n\nThe CHANGELOG.md has been written with full details of all changes, technical decisions, issues encountered, and test results."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":559,"cache_read_input_tokens":121002,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":559,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":331},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d45be86e-3e5a-4433-b76a-a33ae6e615f7","uuid":"2ffaa049-c215-416b-8b65-abfca759aacc"}
